summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Seattle Public Utilities; authorizing the sale and conveyance by Quit Claim Deed of a portion of the City property (Seattle Public Utilities) known as the Lake Youngs Aqueduct Right-of-Way (LYA R/W), all located within the Southwest Quarter of the Southwest Quarter of Section 16, Township 22 North, Range 6 East, W.M., in King County, Washington, and establishing the fair market value thereof.
